snippet.title: SpongeBob: Krusty Cook-Off - Official Pre-Order Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Serve the delicious Krabby Patty to a cast of characters from the SpongeBob SquarePants animated series in this upcoming mobile game, available now for pre-order on the App Store or pre-register the game on Google Play. The game will launch this winter for mobile devices.

#gametrailers #gaming #spongebob
